snippet.title: Johnny Depp loses his Libel case against Amber Heard When Doves Cry
snippet.description:
#PotfsHollywood:Johnny Depp loses his Libel case against Amber Heard When Doves Cry


Depp is also suing Heard because of a 2018 opinion piece published in the Washington Post where she said she was a victim of domestic abuse and how speaking out impacted her career.
